Revision history for Perl extension PPM::Repositories

0.20 Wed Oct 22 2014
     - add activestate repos for 5.14 to 5.20
     - remove activestate HP-UX repos; they seem to be gone
     - add bribes repos for 5.14 to 5.18
     - add sisyphusion repos for 5.16 and 5.18
     - add trouchelle for 5.14
     - add wxperl for 5.16

0.19 Thu Jun 09 2011
    - add 5.14 repos for sisyphusion
    - add 5.14 repos for wxperl

0.18 Mon Dec 06 2010
    - add sisyphusion repository

0.17 Tue May 25 2010
    - add 5.12 repos for bribes, trouchelle and uwinnipeg [RT#57814]
    - add bioperl and bioperl-rc to the old-style interface too
    - prune dead repositories: devhelp, jenda, openi, sablotron

0.16 Tue May 11 2010
    - move test.pl to t/test.t to run it via Test::Harness
    - remove outdated wxansi repository  [RT#55053]
    - add additional architectures for wxperl repo [RT#55053]
    - add ActiveState 64-bit Linux repos
    - add ActivePerl 5.12 repos
    - add bioperl and bioperl-rc repos

0.15  Thu Jun 12 2008
    - add "Paul Miller's Games::RolePlay::MapGen and Gtk2 repository"
      as the "voltar" repository [RT#36254]
    - add note to "gtk2" repo to also check "voltar" repo

0.14  Wed Apr 23 2008
    - Add wxperl and wxansi repositories
    - Rename all 'theory' repositories to 'uwinnipeg'
    - Append '-ppm3' to PPMServer style repositories and remove the
      'S' (for "slower") suffix from the corresponding Website style repos
      for a more consistent overall naming scheme.
    - Rename 'uwinnipeg' to 'uwinnipeg56' for consistency.

0.13  Fri Apr 18 2008
    - devhelp repository has been cleaned up and only contains
      Imager module for 5.8 now.
    - Add devhelp repo to %REPO hash for new API too
    - Add '=head1 NAME' line to properly define the module abstract

0.12  Tue Apr 15 2008
    - removed smueller repository [RT#23979]
    - removed datetime repository [RT#17391]
    - removed dead repositories: soulcage, esoft, savage, spurkis, crazy, dada, rto
    - removed already commented out repositories: xray, perlxml
    - turned jenda's repository to inactive
    - added tcool and trouchelle repositories
    - addded new gtk2 repo; renamed outdated "official" one to gtk2-old
    - added get(), list() and used_archs() function
    - updated documentation
    - added some simple tests to test.pl
    - added sample scripts in eg/ subdirectory

0.11  Thu May 12 04:46:47 2005
    - removed some repositories that are gone for good [RT#12761]

0.10  Thu May 20 15:30:59 2004
    - updated synopsis

0.09  Sat Mar 13 19:08:08 2004
    - some PerlO values were wrong (no biggie)

0.08  Sat Mar 13 17:46:29 2004
    - added smueller, bribes and soulcage/soulcage58 [RT#5367], [RT#5644], [RT#5477]

0.07  Wed Nov  5 20:02:09 2003
    - I realized the 0.05 Changes never happened (D'oh)
    - really added pod pointing to guide(s) on setting up a repository

0.06  Wed Nov  5 19:46:05 2003
    - added esoft
    - added log4perl "repository"
    - updated pod

0.05 
    - added jmcnamara repository (he finally made it a repository)
    - added pod pointing to guide(s) on setting up a repository

0.04  Mon Jun  2 17:28:31 2003
    - marked savage repository active (he finally fixed it)

0.03  Fri May 30 14:43:28 2003
    - added savage repository for 5.8 (which should be active soon),
      fixed up some urls (trailing slash is known to mess up some versions of ppm)

0.02  Tue May 27 05:12:34 2003
